data.description: Out a dirt road awaits this mini farm for you with almost 8 acres to come enjoy! Offering a 5 bedroom/4 bath home with a 40x40 attached 3 bay garage, the home has a 22 panel Generac Solar system to save you money, a 30x30 powered workshop with it's own septic, a 30x60 8 stall barn with 2 tack rooms. The 5th bedroom above the garage is it's own private en-suite. So much to offer, don't miss out!!
